at Olivia's passing.

27:33.443 --> 27:37.118
Olivia Vincent was the Devil Girls.

27:37.823 --> 27:40.372
She had strength...

27:40.909 --> 27:42.582
...beauty...

27:43.620 --> 27:45.793
...class.

27:48.292 --> 27:52.593
She had big ideas
and an even bigger heart.

27:54.756 --> 27:58.260
I know any time
any of us needed advice,

27:58.385 --> 28:03.266
she was the first person we ran to.

28:15.194 --> 28:19.040
I learned a lot from Olivia
these past four years.

28:21.408 --> 28:23.877
I hope that when I'm her age...

28:24.036 --> 28:26.334
...I'm half the woman...

28:26.872 --> 28:29.375
...that sh... That she wa...

28:31.752 --> 28:35.507
