28:39.301 --> 28:41.269
Grief takes many forms.

28:42.137 --> 28:45.107
All we can be sure of is
mourning the loss of a loved one

28:45.224 --> 28:49.320
is a very personal, profound journey.

28:49.937 --> 28:51.484
Matthew 5, verse 4.

28:51.647 --> 28:55.242
"Blessed are those that mourn,
for they shall be comforted."

28:55.734 --> 28:59.784
