29:00.197 --> 29:04.122
...so that we will share that love
when we need it most.

29:04.868 --> 29:07.747
From Him to us...

29:08.413 --> 29:09.790
...through us.

29:11.375 --> 29:13.377
I didn't know Olivia.

29:13.502 --> 29:17.006
But it's a testament to who she was
that you are all here.

29:17.214 --> 29:20.593
May we all mourn her passing,
each of us in our own way.

29:21.051 --> 29:23.270
